==Innovative defenses==
I have never heard of any of these defenses being used successful, or even being presented seriously by any lawyer. If you can find a cite for any of them, we can re-add them. These “defenses” work off flawed understandings of US law and using them will only seriously harm your case and probably get you a contempt charge. --[[User:Cspurrier|Cspurrier]] 21:10, 23 September 2006 (UTC)

